headline: Corebridge Stock Down Despite Q3 Earnings Beat on Fixed Annuity Growth
summary: CRBG's Q3 results reflect increased fixed annuity deposits and higher net investment income, partly offset by higher costs resulting from elevated policyholder benefits.
